<i>Ko'ma Kahless</i>

424
00:20:35,860 --> 00:20:38,362
<i>Ko'ma Kahless</i>

425
00:20:38,404 --> 00:20:41,532
<i>Ko'ma Kahless.</i>

426
00:20:49,916 --> 00:20:53,211
But the Second Dynasty ended
when General K'Trelan

427
00:20:53,252 --> 00:20:55,254
assassinated Emperor Reclaw.

428
00:20:55,295 --> 00:20:58,298
For the next ten years,
the Empire was ruled

429
00:20:58,340 --> 00:21:00,551
by a Council elected
by the people.

430
00:21:00,593 --> 00:21:02,762
Modern-day
Klingon historians

431
00:21:02,803 --> 00:21:05,431
refer to this
as "The Dark Time."

432
00:21:05,472 --> 00:21:09,852
But it's interesting to note
that this first and only

433
00:21:09,894 --> 00:21:11,437
experiment
in Klingon democracy

434
00:21:11,478 --> 00:21:14,190
actually produced
several reforms...

435
00:21:14,232 --> 00:21:16,150
You are straying from the saga.

436
00:21:16,192 --> 00:21:17,818
Am I?

437
00:21:18,945 --> 00:21:22,740
Your task is to recite
the complete chronicle

438
00:21:22,782 --> 00:21:24,825
of the women in my family.

439
00:21:24,867 --> 00:21:26,410
I just thought I'd give you

440
00:21:26,452 --> 00:21:29,288
a broader historical
perspective
along the way.

441
00:21:29,329 --> 00:21:33,084
I am familiar
with Klingon history.

442
00:21:33,126 --> 00:21:38,547
Now, return to the story
of my 23rd maternal grandmother

443
00:21:38,589 --> 00:21:41,675
Shenara,
daughter of Emperor Reclaw

444
00:21:41,717 --> 00:21:43,469
in the Second Dynasty.

445
00:21:43,510 --> 00:21:46,931
Well, that's where we run
into a little bit of a problem.

446
00:21:46,973 --> 00:21:49,016
You see, I did some research

447
00:21:49,058 --> 00:21:51,351
and when Emperor Reclaw
was killed,

448
00:21:51,393 --> 00:21:54,021
all of the members
of the Imperial Family

449
00:21:54,063 --> 00:21:56,607
were put to death,
including Shenara.

450
00:21:56,649 --> 00:21:59,860
When the Third Dynasty
was founded ten years later,

451
00:21:59,902 --> 00:22:02,488
a new group of Klingons
were given the titles

452
00:22:02,529 --> 00:22:06,450
and the names of the original
Imperial Family...

453
00:22:06,492 --> 00:22:09,411
to create the<i> illusion</i>
of an unbroken line.

454
00:22:09,453 --> 00:22:11,998
So, the woman
that you think of

455
00:22:12,039 --> 00:22:14,834
as your 23rd
maternal grandmother...

456
00:22:14,875 --> 00:22:17,003
isn't related to you at all.

457
00:22:17,044 --> 00:22:20,589
Your real ancestor's name
was Karana,

458
00:22:20,631 --> 00:22:24,135
a concubine living outside
the Imperial Stables.

459
00:22:24,177 --> 00:22:27,596
My grandmother's name
was Shenara.

460
00:22:27,638 --> 00:22:29,723
That may be
what's been passed down

461
00:22:29,765 --> 00:22:33,936
from generation to generation,
but it has no basis in fact.

462
00:22:33,978 --> 00:22:35,855
But who cares about facts?

463
00:22:35,896 --> 00:22:39,399
The chronicle says
that you have
Imperial blood in your veins,

464
00:22:39,441 --> 00:22:42,402
and that's exactly what
we'll keep telling everyone.

465
00:22:45,823 --> 00:22:49,160
Continue with the saga.

466
00:22:49,202 --> 00:22:51,453
My pleasure.

467
00:22:53,539 --> 00:22:55,124
Hey, Major.

468
00:22:55,166 --> 00:22:56,917
Is it true Dax is having
a party tomorrow night?

469
00:22:56,959 --> 00:22:58,336
Ah, news travels fast.

470
00:22:58,376 --> 00:22:59,712
Well, is it by
invitation or...?

471
00:22:59,753 --> 00:23:01,172
I'm sure you're welcome.

472
00:23:01,214 --> 00:23:02,798
And you can tell Nog
the same goes for him, too.

473
00:23:02,840 --> 00:23:05,383
Great.
Oh, I understand
congratulations are in order

474
00:23:05,425 --> 00:23:07,345
to our newest
published author.

475
00:23:07,385 --> 00:23:08,637
Thank you.

476
00:23:13,391 --> 00:23:14,560
What was all that about?

477
00:23:14,601 --> 00:23:15,519
Nothing.

478
00:23:15,561 --> 00:23:17,395
There they go.

479
00:23:18,898 --> 00:23:20,566
KIRA:
They look so serious.

480
00:23:20,607 --> 00:23:22,068
It's all an act.

481
00:23:22,109 --> 00:23:23,652
They don't want
the rest of us to know

482
00:23:23,694 --> 00:23:26,239
